Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.74,0:01:03.86,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that some Raira Academy \Nstudents were attacked by the Slasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.86,0:01:06.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But make her body the center of it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:10.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And throw those around her into the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:11.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruna, did you make sure to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:13.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest in Ikebukuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:14.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.41,0:01:17.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I weren't the headless rider, I'd be dead right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.33,0:01:19.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'm gonna kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:21.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hunt him down and kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.01,0:01:22.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:55.71,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm flying...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:57.51,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm flying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.12,0:02:11.66,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,All I wanted was to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.22,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,About Ikebukuro;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:18.95,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,about the source of energy for this refuse-packed city,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:22.95,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,about the truth behind this city that \Ncontinues to swell with desire every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.04,0:02:24.34,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,That's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:27.00,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And...about the strongest man in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.95,0:02:32.00,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,About six months ago, I was writing a seasonal \Nfeature story about the troubled times in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:35.17,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And I met a man while researching the \Nlegendary strongest person in Ikebukuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:40.43,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The air; the air around him was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:42.54,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only way I can describe—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:46.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You ass, making me resort to violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:49.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a god?! Are you just pretending to be one?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:51.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shizuo, we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:55.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:58.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.00,0:02:59.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That teacher who sexually harasses his students.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:04.32,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:13.46,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Amidst my everyday life of writing gossip articles for a third-rate \Nmagazine, he'd revived that pure feeling I'd felt during my younger days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:15.07,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,A curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.07,0:03:18.34,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, an intense curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:20.69,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to know everything about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:21.38,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:26.26,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the uproar that followed soon after, my article was postponed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:33.23,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the specifics of the incident, but it seemed \Nthere were more evil spirits writhing in this magic capital...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:38.65,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And something was about to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:44.88,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this strongest man had to be involved in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:47.45,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,As I'd resumed reporting for that feature article on Ikebukuro,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:51.25,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to start collecting information from those around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:53.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Shizuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:57.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have some salmon roe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:04:00.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, I didn't order that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:04.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Shizuo's friends are my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:07.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your purchase.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:10.25,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he use that kind of Japanese on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:15.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.80,0:04:18.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:20.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuo's a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:23.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever seen him in the middle of a fight or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:25.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, fighting isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:27.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Peace is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:28.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:32.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Giant clam is good?\N One order of giant clam!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:34.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:36.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:39.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Simon's a pacifist, so there's no use talking about fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:44.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was just asking him who the strongest person in the city is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.00,0:04:49.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should ask a field expert about something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:53.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really want to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:04.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest in Ikebukuro, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:09.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I heard from someone that you're \Nparticularly knowledgeable of matters in this field.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:15.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're talking about fights, you do understand that that era has already passed, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:19.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We now use our brains more than our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:22.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's clean work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:23.16,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,"Clean," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.16,0:05:26.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, were someone to make us look like fools, that'd be the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:31.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone wants to start a fight, then it doesn't matter whether \Nthey're an amateur, they have a blade, or they try to muscle us out;
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:33.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll thoroughly crush them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:36.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:44.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who act out are amateur brats, not pros like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:47.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, like the Dollars or the Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:52.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as long as they don't interfere with our business, we won't touch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:58.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, people of urban legend like the \Nheadless rider or the Slasher have appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:00.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, I guess it's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:03.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest person in this city is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:04.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Heiwajima Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:06.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you do think it's him, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:09.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard he puts up a clean fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:14.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, there's an information dealer who's more knowledgeable about this kind of thing than we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:16.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:17.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please introduce me to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:20.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm asking for anything in return...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:24.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, as for our line of business...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:26.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:31.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who told you about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:38.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't reveal my sources...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:39.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:44.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here for that "troubled times in Tokyo" thing, right? They \Nshowcase things like strange happenings and gang member introductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:46.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the next issue's about Ikebukuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:48.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you know all that, that makes things easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:53.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm thinking of writing an article that \Ndecides who the strongest person in Ikebukuro is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:55.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:58.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are tons of strong people in that city...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:01.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In a bare-fisted fight, it would be Simon from that sushi place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:04.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If there aren't any rules, it'd be Shizu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:07.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shizu-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:08.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean Heiwajima Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:11.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to ask about him, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:12.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:14.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As for Shizuo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:15.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:16.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:19.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's enough for me just to know something about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:22.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I try to learn some things about him since I'm no good at dealing with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.59,0:07:25.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's unpleasant, so I don't want to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.58,0:07:27.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please try?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:30.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Mr. Niekawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:32.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How's your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:37.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As her parent, you must have been worried \Nthat she had to transfer over something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:43.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the magazine writer who, six months ago, came into contact \Nwith Heiwajima Shizuo and ended up in the sky along with a streetlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:46.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go sniffing out things around that city,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:49.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you might end up interfering with my work...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:50.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:52.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you're already aware of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:56.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But there have been some dangerous occurrences in that city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:08:00.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they have anything to do with the conflict \Nbetween the Dollars and the Yellow Scarves—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:04.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's part of it, as are the Slasher incidents that started it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:05.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Slasher?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:09.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though there's already one uncontrollable urban legend here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:11.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:16.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to know more about Heiwajima\NShizuo, I can introduce you to a close friend of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:21.49,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Orihara the information dealer \Nintroduced me to a rather odd individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:22.93,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, here's a piece of advice:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:26.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't talk to Shizuo about his younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:29.40,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I'd known that six months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:34.10,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I was caught off-guard by the mention of my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:36.89,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a daughter who's in her second year of high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:40.86,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been living by ourselves since my wife ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:44.11,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I don't think she looks up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:50.80,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the reason I started writing articles just for the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:55.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, I'm Celty the courier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:08:59.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:04.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuo's a trustworthy friend. At least to me he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:07.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he can be scary when you make him mad, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:12.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm planning to write about who the best fighter is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:16.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The magazine you work for really likes that kind of thing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:17.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You publish motorcycle gang rankings and whatnot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:19.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:26.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, there are some people around town \Nwho'd consider you the strongest person here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:28.08,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she's laughing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:32.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As if! Shizuo's way stronger than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:35.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so insane it's almost moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:36.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I put this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:38.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just about fighting or combat styles...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:42.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you'd understand if I said he's a lone wolf or has magic powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:43.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe, "He's an alien?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:44.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't quite work...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:47.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like a little gray alien experienced something traumatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:51.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, no matter how well-trained a fighter you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:52.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if you get shot, you're done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:53.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:55.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His strength is like that of a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Comparing them was nonsense from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:57.61,Secondary Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I was moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:10:01.75,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd experienced Heiwajima Shizuo's strength with my own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:06.20,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,For an urban legend herself to speak so highly of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:09.46,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, that strength is of another dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:12.65,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps, due to a cranial process involving adrenaline...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:14.71,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He's able to utilize some supreme power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:20.09,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The momentary power that transcends the \Nlimits of humans is completely off the charts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:22.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:26.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...this is just out of curiosity, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:27.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:32.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, could you please show me what's under your helmet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:33.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to if you don't—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:45.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:50.96,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it; Ms. Celty must be a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:54.25,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,After I pulled myself together, I continued my investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:58.19,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept hearing rumors about the rivalry \Nbetween the Dollars and the Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:11:02.60,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that the leader of the Yellow Scarves—their shogun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:04.39,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Would move on the Dollars, who assume they're being ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:06.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what kind of guy is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:08.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:11.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt the young members of the Yellow Scarves know, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:19.44,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I know about the shogun's true identity is that \Nhe's ordered everyone not to get involved with Orihara Izaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:20.36,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:23.87,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That strongest...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:29.25,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The recurring Slasher incidents...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:33.35,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The Yellow Scarves apparently believe that the Dollars are behind it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:39.80,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard that a single girl was spared in the incident a few \Ndays ago, where some high school girls were attacked here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:44.80,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I unconsciously likened that girl to my own daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:48.47,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,A father who'd risk his life to protect his daughter from the Slasher...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:54.65,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,However, right now my daughter is like an \Nalien to me who I have no hope of understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:55.65,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:58.73,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the day I go face-to-face...with the daughter I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:15.28,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:17.22,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,The victim of today's Slasher attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:21.70,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Was apparently writing an article on \NTokyo's troubled times for "Tokyo Warrior."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:22.75,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:24.87,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's a magazine journalist?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:26.89,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.92,0:12:30.06,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon...have I ever lied to you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:31.71,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:33.77,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know him, Setton?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:35.23,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:37.69,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a fan of the article.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:40.02,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, maybe I should read it sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:41.89,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that's pretty scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:44.65,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish the police the best of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:45.57,ASS Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,165)}Saika has entered the chat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:46.74,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:47.25,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:47.77,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:48.78,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I Cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:50.45,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,It cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:51.44,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I Cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:54.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who wants to cut you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:56.33,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Still, No Good,,, Strong People, Like
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:58.33,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Evenin', Saika.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:01.92,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, Setton. It won't reply to anything we say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:02.71,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to cut, more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.58,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,That's rather eerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.58,0:13:06.88,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Cutting people and all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.88,0:13:08.55,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,With this whole Slasher thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.13,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:10.93,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:11.77,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Strong People,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:12.56,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Want To love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:13.35,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I Found.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:13.81,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:14.14,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Love
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:14.77,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Found
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:15.49,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:16.43,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.43,0:13:18.20,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Heiwajima Shizuo,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:19.40,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.87,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know Shizuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:29.78,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Heiwajima
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:33.11,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:34.59,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:35.36,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I Love
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:36.61,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I Love, Shizuo, I Love.\N Cut Heiwajima Shizuo. I, Love Heiwajima Shizuo, Cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:37.10,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Heiwajima, Shizuo, Cut, Love, Heiwajima, Cut, Cut
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.10,0:13:37.91,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Love, Heiwajima Shizuo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.91,0:13:38.48,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,My Mother's Wish, Heiwajima,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:39.09,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,My Mother's Wish, Shizuo, My Mother's Wish, Shizuo, I Love
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:39.66,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Heiwajima, My Mother's Wish, I Cut
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:40.01,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I Love, Shizuo,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:40.68,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I Cut, I Love, Heiwajima, I Love,,, I Cut
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:41.27,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Cut, Heiwajima
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:41.73,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I Love, Shizuo, My Mother's Wish
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:42.44,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,My Mother's Wish
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:43.76,ASS Chat 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuo,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:45.13,ASS Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Saika has left the chat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:01.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up, Anri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:02.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get fat, Anri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:06.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright, I'll just exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:09.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was joking. Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:12.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be together forever, won't we, Mom and Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:23.05,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl had a dream every night...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:26.80,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Of a happy family; one you'd find in a drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:29.55,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,However, that was a fleeting illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:32.52,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Her parents died five years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:34.56,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,In a horrible accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.16,0:14:39.31,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,As the only survivor, she still has those dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:43.40,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams of that happy family she never had.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:46.53,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The tragedy that stole her parents away...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:52.16,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the first incident the Slasher ever caused.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:55.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anri...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:57.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already making preparations for the sports festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:14:59.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:00.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:03.83,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She thought she was a cunning person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:06.03,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She could plainly see what his ulterior motive was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:08.01,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet she never faced it head-on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.54,0:15:12.99,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd close off her heart and simply wait for the situation to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:15.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...might come after you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:16.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to go out alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:18.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sexually harassing her again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:20.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have that now, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:24.81,Secondary Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She knew that she was leeching off of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:22.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Masaomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.91,0:15:24.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonohara!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:27.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Enter the coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:29.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Were you waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:32.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd turn into a fossil waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:33.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:33.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Square root of three points.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:36.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A square root? What's a square root?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:40.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At least make your criticism easy to understand with something like "minus twenty points."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:44.12,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,When I awoke, I was in a hospital bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:47.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. You'll get better if you just take it easy for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:51.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to stay here for about one week, and after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:53.22,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a gap...in my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:56.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you shouldn't get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:59.72,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time for this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.98,0:15:59.72,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait Mr. Niekawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:02.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:03.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:05.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:14.28,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside me told me to "watch over her."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:18.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Niekawa from room five still hasn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:19.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:21.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope his wounds don't open back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:35.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:27.95,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuo,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:31.23,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate your concern, but you don't have to come if you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:33.45,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my own problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:36.44,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,First off, the Slasher won't necessarily be out tonight—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.44,0:16:38.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive that Slasher bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:42.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's an ethereal sword or something else, breaking a katana means it dies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:44.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although even if it doesn't die, I'll kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:47.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:47.61,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:55.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:58.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time to get involved with guys like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:02.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have something to say, you insect?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:06.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like to say hello to that cockroach over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:09.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, looks can kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:10.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:21.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's at least a 0.000000000000000675% \Nchance that someone can die from a curse or a stare.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.07,0:17:21.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:23.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How many zeros was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:26.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, bartender...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:28.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A b-bartender...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:29.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:33.48,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,So you can't complain if I hurl you into the air and you die, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.18,0:17:44.90,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Niekawa Haruna...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:49.13,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,What was with Mr. Nasujima's reaction...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:51.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:54.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already eleven o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.45,0:17:56.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for students to be going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:02.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:04.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go home right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:06.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:08.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you live around here, I can take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:12.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:16.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've received an emergency call stating that a fight has broken out in Eastern Ikebukuro Central Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:17.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been dispatched, so please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:20.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. We're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:22.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Mr. Kuzuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:28.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel like it, just wait at the police \Nbox and I'll take you home when I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:44.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:50.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop thinking that replacing the normal characters for "moment" with more pretentious ones will make the sentence look cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:54.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're were that age where you wanted to look at \Nthings from a different angle, weren't you, Yuma-chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:57.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And stop thinking that simply by rejecting the worldview of a normal adult
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:19:00.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that it will score you points with middle and high \Nschool students going through their rebellious stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:05.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking that rejecting philosophy and society \Nwill make you look cool is so shallow, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:09.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty rare for Yumasaki to be bad-mouthing a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:11.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.78,0:19:12.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.76,0:19:16.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A novel that he self-published a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:21.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I might not be in a position to say anything, since I \Nwas sleeping, but one of our comrades was attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:22.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be serious about gathering our information.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.27,0:19:27.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, unlike Kaztano, we don't even know this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:30.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they are a member of the Dollars...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:34.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At least try to sympathize with others a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:36.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's sad, but I've locked that feeling away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:39.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to forgive the Slasher, but I've locked that feeling away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:43.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, why did we join the Dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:45.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to lead peaceful lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:50.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to have a cute, green-haired daughter in a foreign land...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:54.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And when we return to Japan, I'll live happily with three beautiful sisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:56.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if such a modest life were possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:19:58.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that "Yotsuba&!"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:01.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, it was around here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:02.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The place where the Slasher appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:04.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a reckless kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.98,0:20:06.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the type of kid who's most susceptible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:09.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, this might be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:10.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:12.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:15.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy back there had red eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:16.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.84,0:20:31.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:32.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:34.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just reliving a traumatic experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:42.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:56.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Togusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:20:57.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.35,0:21:02.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Floor it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:07.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:10.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are we going, Celty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:12.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:15.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're horrible, Kadota!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:18.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how you act right after saying you want to live in peace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:21.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.43,0:21:22.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, it was self-defense...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.11,0:21:43.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:01.62,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The headless rider and...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.62,0:22:02.67,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.40,0:22:06.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dotachin! He's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.06,0:22:08.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you some kind of monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:12.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...Heiwajima Shizuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:15.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've wanted to meet you, Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:18.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've wanted to meet you, Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.09,0:22:18.97,Secondary Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Heiwajima Shizuo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.97,0:22:23.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you very, very, very, very much, Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.78,0:22:25.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. I'm going to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:32.49,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I'm going to interview Heiwajima Shizuo, the strongest...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.79,0:22:36.70,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can write a good article, everything's bound to go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.70,0:22:38.33,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,My wife will come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:41.00,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,My strained relationship with my daughter will get better, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.50,0:22:42.75,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be like the good ol' days...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:44.00,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.20,0:24:18.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Slasher incidents were supposed to have ended after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.10,0:24:20.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet they didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.35,0:24:23.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, it signaled the beginning of her destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.38,0:24:26.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's turned into a long, long night.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.08,0:24:29.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time: Mutual Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.01,0:24:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
